{"id":"353300","title":"华与诚之诗（出书版）","writer":"黯然销魂蛋/黯然销混蛋","dateline":"1534266736","updatetime":"1534266736","isover":"1","filesize":"169153","linecount":"1372","wordcount":"83050","imgpath":"https://photos.smugmug.com/photos/i-J5m4QFg/0/48c64242/S/i-J5m4QFg-S.jpg","hash":"huayuchengzhishi","urlhash":"txtnvl_299510","sign":"","desc":"台倍乐出版繁体坚排\n混蛋工厂011\n定价250元\n2008年7月21日出版\n文案：\n（永乐町69号系列）\n禁锢  宣判的刑期是千年\n背叛烙印了无可饶恕的重罪\n戴著不允许解脱的枷锁\n残暴而美艳\n开到荼糜的华与诚之诗\n也许只是\n爱与恨都凋零了很久以后\n没有赎尽的罚\n相关文： 《永乐町69号（出书版）》作者：黯然销魂蛋/黯然销混蛋","hot":"0","num":"0","cid":"14","suggcate":"耽美现代,耽美","suggcids":"14,121","notbook":"0","fetchv":"0","lasthot":"0","clicknum":"0","isvip":"0","ish":"1","age":"古代","channel":"女","isqiniu":"0","list":"0,34i,6p3,al6,ei4,i1f,lmd,ozw,ss5,w37,108q,13sl,176r,1auj,1dv8,1gux,1jtw,1n33,1qnq,1tsl,1xy0,21eh,24sx,28k9,2cfd,2g9r,2k1f,2my1,2o89","pages":"28","errors":"0","stars":"0","starcounts":"0","isbroken":"0","iswx":"1","leader":"莲华|夜山|山诚司|邪丸|森濑","txturl":"https://photos.smugmug.com/photos/i-4BW3WFC/0/efadf873/1500x1500/i-4BW3WFC-1500x1500.png","startpos":"10148"}